</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="597" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="2.[132,1338,2512,3092]" pageId="2" pageNumber="597">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[135,480,2901,2934]" pageId="2" pageNumber="597">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Anderson’s Shrew Mole is known only from a few locations, and there is no information about its population status, habitat preferences, ecology, or conservation threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
